data.description:
What a great value for this Stunning home. Features many upgrades Like Granite Countertops, Hardwood and luxury vinyl flooring, maple cabinets.  Gourmet kitchen island with seating, overlooking the Family room and Sunroom. Great for entertaining or daily family activities.  You will love the spacious bedrooms. The oversize owner's suite offers a beautiful tray ceiling, large walk n closet, private bath with double sinks, and separate tub and shower. 
There is loft space on the second floor, that could be a fourth bedroom, office, workout area, family room or more. The basement is waiting for your touch to be whatever you desire it to be. basement is plumbed for a bath. Private back yard with stone patio.  and new viny privacy fence.  Washer and Dryer are negotiable. All furniture is available to purchase.
